	s/trace_bitmap/trace_checksum/.

	* include/freetype/internal/fttrace.h: s/bitmap/checksum/.

	* src/base/ftobjs.c (FT_COMPONENT): s/trace_bitmap/trace_checksum/.
	Adjust code.

